- set_meta_tags(get_meta_tags("About Us","About the Advlo Team","Christopher Knight, Shayan Dhanani, Jonathan Maser, Advlo Founders"))

#about
  - image_chris = "background/about_chris.jpg"
  - image_jon = "background/about_jon.jpg"
  - image_shayan = "background/about_shayan.jpg"

  .row
    .col-md-4
      .personal_img{style: "background: url(#{image_path image_chris}) center center no-repeat"}

      .row.text-center 
        %h3 CHRISTOPHER
        %h4 The Anthropologist Programmer

    .col-md-4
      .personal_img{style: "background: url(#{image_path image_jon}) center center no-repeat"}

      .row.text-center
        %h3 JON
        %h4 The Entreprenuerial Thrillseeker
    .col-md-4
      .personal_img{style: "background: url(#{image_path image_shayan}) center center no-repeat"}

      .row.text-center
        %h3 SHAYAN
        %h4 The Exploring Scientist


  .border
  .border

  .about-wrapper
    .container
      %p.text-center.mission_statement
        Our goal is to connect adventure travelers around the world with the most authentic locals. We have built the platform as something we want to use ourselves, and for the incredible guides around the globe who deserve to be seen. 
            
  .col.md-12.text-center.press
    .container
      %h3 FEATURED IN

      .row
        .col-md-2
          %a{href: "http://www.tnooz.com/article/startup-pitch-advlo-connects-adventure-seekers-locals/", target: "_blank"}
            .mention.tnooz= image_tag 'icons/press/tnooz.png'
        .col-md-2
          %a{href: "http://adventuretravel.about.com/od/Adventure-Travel-General/fl/New-Online-Marketplace-Invites-Travelers-to-Adventure-with-Locals.htm", target: "_blank"}
            .mention.about= image_tag 'icons/press/about.png'
        .col-md-2
          %a{href: "http://www.tetonsports.com/adventureblog/lets-change-way-travel-adventure-locals/", target: "_blank"}
            .mention.teton= image_tag 'icons/press/teton.png'
        .col-md-2
          %a{href: "http://skift.com/2014/06/09/5-new-travel-startups-that-help-tourist-explore-the-outdoors/#3", target: "_blank"}
            .mention.skift= image_tag 'icons/press/skift.png'
        .col-md-2
          %a{href: "http://clapway.tv/needs-tour-guides-advlo-helps-adventure-locals/", target: "_blank"}
            .mention.clapway= image_tag 'icons/press/clapway.png'
        .col-md-2
          %a{href: "http://tech.co/advlo-launches-adventure-travel-platform-2014-09", target: "_blank"}
            .mention.techco= image_tag 'icons/press/techco.png'


  .border

  .white_background.container-fluid.about-bio-brick
    .col-md-4
      .row.text-center 
        .text-brick.self-bio
          When I think about my experiences from traveling my fondest memories are not about what I did, but from the people I adventured with. Travel is a luxury that most of the world's people never get to experience. However, the ability to immerse yourself into a foreign culture has been the greatest learning experience I have ever had.
          %p{style: "color: #C35B26; margin-top: 10px;"}
            = "- CHRISTOPHER"

          

    .col-md-4
      .row.text-center
        .text-brick.self-bio
          Connection stems from shared experiences. 
          After traveling around the world, experiencing diverse cultures and meeting some of the most genuine locals, I wanted to make connecting travelers to amazing adventurers an easier process. If you love travel, people and unique experiences as much as I do, you're going to love Advlo.
          %p{style: "color: #C35B26; margin-top: 10px;"}
            = "- JON"


    .col-md-4
      .row.text-center
        .text-brick.self-bio
          The world is an extremely diverse place, and I truly believe that the only way to experience and learn about what it has to offer is by interacting with those whom have spent a majority of their life there. Every person's experience is different when they travel, for me the cultural exchange along with learning from the locals will have me traveling for a while.
          %p{style: "color: #C35B26; margin-top: 10px;"}
            = "- SHAYAN"



    .col-md-12.text-center
      .row#contact-us
        #leave-a-note
          %p Leave us a Note

    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.text-center#contact-advlo
      %form{"accept-charset" => "UTF-8", action: "/contact", method: "POST", id: "about_us_contact_form", "data-remote" => "true"}
        = tag(:input, :type => "hidden", :name => request_forgery_protection_token.to_s, :value => form_authenticity_token)
        = tag(:input, :type => "hidden", :name => "about_us", :value => true)

        - if current_user
          = tag(:input, :type => "hidden", :name => "contact[user_id]", :value => current_user.id)

        .form-group.row
          %input.form-control{type: "text", name: "contact[email]", id: "contact_email", placeholder: 'Email Address', class: "email-field", value: current_user ? current_user.email : ''}

        .form-group.row
          %textarea.form-control{rows: "7", type: "text", name: "contact[comments]", id: "contact_comments", placeholder: 'We would love to hear from you.'}

        #honeypot
          %input.form-control{type: "text", name: "honeypot", id: "honeypot", placeholder: 'This field is like a captcha for bots.. Do not fill in.'}
          
        .row.text-center
          .btn.btn-primary#about-us-contact Submit

  .border
          
